ign\">[δόρυ] ἐ. ἐπ᾽ ἄκρης,</foreign> of the Trojan horse, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:8:508\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">8.508</biblScope> </bibl> ; freq. of the dead, <pb n=\"694\" TEIform=\"pb\"/> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">νεκρόν, νεκροὺς ἐ.,</foreign> of the friends, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">drag</tr_> them <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">away, rescue</tr_> them, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:5:573\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.573</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:16:781\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">16.781</biblScope> </bibl> ; of the enemy, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">drag</tr_> them <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">off for plunder, ransom,</tr_> etc., <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:4:467\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.467</biblScope></bibl>, al.; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τρὶς ἐρύσας περὶ σῆμα</foreign> (sc. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">Ἕκτορα</foreign>) <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:24:16\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">24.16</biblScope> </bibl> ; of dogs and birds of prey, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">drag and tear,</tr_> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">οἰωνοὶ ὠμησταὶ ἐρύουσι</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:11:454\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">11.454</biblScope></bibl></cit>, etc.; <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">drag away, carry off violently,</tr_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:9:99\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\"